c Alef-A Vowels as Regular Syllables
  'እ' + any(ካዕብ-key) > 'ኡ'
  'እ' + any(ሣልስ-key) > 'ኢ'
  'እ' + any(ራብዕ-key) > 'ኣ'
  'ኢ' + any(ግዕዝ-key) > 'ኤ'
  'እ' + any(ሳብዕ-key) > 'ኦ'

c Aynu-A Vowels as Regular Syllables
  'እ' + any(ግዕዝ-key) > 'ዕ'
  'ዕ' + any(ግዕዝ-key) > 'ዐ'
  'ዕ' + any(ካዕብ-key) > 'ዑ'
  'ዕ' + any(ሣልስ-key) > 'ዒ'
  'ዕ' + any(ራብዕ-key) > 'ዓ'
